                    </div>
                    <span>If you want to learn how to exploit software, this is is a MUST for your library. An awesome book despite a few errors in the text.
<br />
<br />The only issue I have is with the numerous promises of additional resources on the web site that have never materialized.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Be Familiar with C, assembly, and computer architectures</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
